title = "Document Classification"
+++

Classifiying documents automatically is one of the main activities for effectively managing text and unstructured information.

Also referred to as categorization, clustering or text classification, automatic document classification allows you to divide and organize text based on a set of predefined categories that allow rapid, easy retrieval of information in the search phase.

Assignning meaningful topics to your texts never been easier. Zaal enables you to 
automatically find the abstract topics of your text using a RESTful API.
